    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for zipping around town or hitting the highway for a weekend getaway. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it drives like a dream! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
