    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride of ownership, offering a refined driving experience that remains tight and responsive. The exterior paint retains a brilliant gloss, complemented by well-preserved alloy wheels, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood from highway commuting. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features high-quality upholstery that has been meticulously vacuumed and conditioned; the driver\u2019s seat shows only minimal softening of the side bolsters. Every feature, from the intuitive infotainment system to the panoramic sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and dry, benefiting from a documented history of timely fluid changes and a recently replaced battery. It handles beautifully with no rattles or vibrations, making it an excellent find for a discerning buyer looking for a reliable, high-quality vehicle.",
      "price": 34800.0,
